# Sweet Potato Tots

Based on [Yummy Toddler Food](https://www.yummytoddlerfood.com/favorite-sweet-potato-tots) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251208235133/https://www.yummytoddlerfood.com/favorite-sweet-potato-tots/)) and [Mama Knows Nutrition](https://mamaknowsnutrition.com/recipes/sweet-potato-tater-tots-recipe-for-kids) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251006131728/https://mamaknowsnutrition.com/recipes/sweet-potato-tater-tots-recipe-for-kids/))

